cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image processing and semantic scene completion. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as the completion of 3D scenes is relevant to robotics applications. The use of a light-weight network and multi-scale fusion mechanism suggests that machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories are also possible. Finally, the paper may belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with 3D shape completion and segmentation.
